{"article_id":"nDrWJeELZPYmoTfM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Steps by the Chinese and Hong Kong governments in recent years have raised unease among Hong Kong residents about their future ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"a concern","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"that burst out in a protest by hundreds of thousands of people last weekend .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Many in the semiautonomous Chinese territory worry","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"the freedoms","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"they enjoy under a `` one-country , two-systems '' framework","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"are eroding ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"as both governments use carrots and sticks","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"to draw Hong Kong into China 's orbit .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"The former British colony was returned to China in 1997 under the framework ,","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"which guarantees it the right","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"to retain its own social , legal and political systems for 50 years .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"A look at major events :","depth":2},{"id":13,"text":"July 2003 :","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"In the largest protest since the handover , hundreds of thousands marched against proposed national security legislation","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that would have criminalized `` subversion '' against the Chinese government .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Hong Kong residents saw the move as an affront to the region 's autonomy ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"and the bill was subsequently withdrawn .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"September-December 2014 :","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Protesters","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"seeking direct elections for Hong Kong 's leader","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"lay siege to government headquarters for 79 days","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"but fail to win any concessions .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The movement inspires a new generation of political activists","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"but also builds cynicism about the power of popular movements","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to effect political change .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"October 2015 :","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Four people","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"connected with a Hong Kong publisher and bookshop","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that published books","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"banned in China","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"go missing .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"A fifth person disappears in December .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Chinese authorities later say","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"they were detained for investigations into criminal activity .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"The case raises questions about freedom of expression in Hong Kong .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"January 2018 :","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Gui Minhai , one of the booksellers","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"who disappeared in 2015 ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"is arrested on a train in China","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"while traveling with two Swedish diplomats .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Gui ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"a Swedish citizen , had been released in October 2017 .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"September 2018 :","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"A high-speed rail link opens between Hong Kong and mainland China .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Passengers clear Chinese immigration inside the station in Hong Kong ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"prompting protests from some opposition lawmakers","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that Chinese law would apply in the immigration area .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"September 2018 :","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Hong Kong bans the Hong Kong National Party ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"which advocates independence for the territory ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"on national security grounds .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"The ban is seen as an unprecedented step","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"to quash separatist voices .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"October 2018 :","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Hong Kong-based Financial Times editor Victor Mallet has his application","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"to renew his work visa","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"rejected .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Authorities wo n't say","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"why ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"but it comes","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"after Mallet introduced the leader of the Hong Kong National Party at a Foreign Correspondents ' Club event in August .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"October 2018 :","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"China 's President Xi Jinping presides over ceremony","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"opening a 55-kilometer","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"( 34-mile )","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"-","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"long bridge","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"linking Hong Kong and Macau to the mainland .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"February 2019 :","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"China announces plans","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"to create a Greater Bay Area","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"encompassing Hong Kong , Macau and neighboring Guandong province in the mainland","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"to foster economic development .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"The move is seen as an effort","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"to deepen ties among Hong Kong , Macau and the mainland .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"April 2019 :","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Lam 's government introduces amendments to Hong Kong 's extradition laws","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"that would allow criminal suspects to be extradited to China .","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"Opponents say","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"the changes would damage the territory 's legal independence","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"and suspects would not be guaranteed fair trials .","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"April 2019 :","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"A Hong Kong court convicts nine leaders of the 2014 pro-democracy demonstrations","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"known as the `` Umbrella Movement . ''","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"Hong Kong judges were reportedly under pressure from China to hand down heavy sentences","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"to deter future protests .","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"June 2019 :","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Hundreds of thousands march through central Hong Kong","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"to protest the proposed changes to the extradition laws .","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":179,"left":101,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":92,"right":100,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":0,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":97,"right":99,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":95,"right":96,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":3,"right":94,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":93,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":9,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":12,"right":177,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":177,"left":105,"right":176,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":13,"right":104,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":102,"right":103,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":112,"right":175,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":18,"right":111,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":108,"right":110,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"